## 🤖 AI Features

- **Claude Haiku** generates personalized story continuations per child
- Prompt engineered for Islamic safety and age-appropriate content
- **Offline fallback** — app fully works without an API key

---

## 📊 Gamification System

- ⚡ **XP Points** — 35–50 XP per completed mission
- 🎯 **8 Levels** — Little Seeker → Jannah Seeker
- 🏅 **6 Badges** — Unlocked by XP milestones
- 📈 **Progress Bars** — Per world and per level

