## ☁️ Deploy to Streamlit Cloud (Free)

1. Push to GitHub
2. Go to [share.streamlit.io](https://share.streamlit.io)
3. Connect your repo → set `app.py` as entry point
4. Add `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` in Secrets
5. Deploy → Live in ~60 seconds!

